Applications have been invited from unemployed SC/ST candidates for availing themselves of loan under the microcredit self-employment scheme being implemented by State SC/ST Development Corporation. Loans up to Rs.50,000 would be available under the scheme. The applicants should be aged between 18 and 50 years and should have an annual family income not exceeding Rs.98,000 in rural areas and Rs.1,20,000 in urban areas. The loan has to be repaid within three years with 5 per cent interest. More details are available at the office of the corporation at Thirumala.â€” Special Correspondent